title: Emily Ratajkowski Doesn’t Care If You Call Her A Bad Feminist | Forbes

media:group.media:title: Emily Ratajkowski Doesn’t Care If You Call Her A Bad Feminist | Forbes
media:group.media:description:
Ratajkowski knows that she courts controversy for talking about women’s empowerment while also building a career centered around her body and sexuality. She doesn’t agree, but has come to terms with it.

Forbes Women Editor Maggie McGrath spoke with Ratajkowski at the 2022 Forbes Power Women's Summit.

Read the full story on Forbes: https://www.forbes.com/sites/maggiemcgrath/2022/11/01/emily-ratajkowski-doesnt-care-if-you-call-her-a-bad-feminist/?sh=9c79ea612749
